data.description: Paradise Awaits at 3614 Ebb Tide Lane!Live the dream in this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home in beautiful Gulf Breeze, Florida. Perfect for enjoying coastal living at its finest, this property boasts not only comfortable living space but also unparalleled access to the water.Effortless Accessibility: Enjoy the convenience of an in-home elevator, making every floor easily accessible.Unwind by the Water: Step out your back door and onto your own private pier, ideal for fishing, crabbing, or simply soaking up the stunning waterfront views. Imagine relaxing on your pier with a cool drink in hand, watching the sunset paint the sky in vibrant hues.Prime Gulf Breeze Location: Situated in a desirable Gulf Breeze neighborhood.
